'''Telltale Tool'''是[[诉说游戏|诉说游戏]]公司以[[Lua|Lua]]脚本语言自主开发的[[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mixnmojo.com/news/Telltale-Makes-Games-For-Everything |publisher=[[The_International_House_of_Mojo|The International House of Mojo]] |title=Telltale Makes Games For Everything |date=2013-08-27 |accessdate=2013-09-17 |archive-date=2019-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926121158/https://mixnmojo.com/news/Telltale-Makes-Games-For-Everything |dead-url=no }}</ref>它採用可移植設計，使得诉说游戏能够同时在多个平台发布和更新游戏。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.penny-arcade.com/report/article/upscaling-for-tablets-how-telltale-planned-for-the-ios-release-of-the-walki |title=Upscaling for tablets: how Telltale planned for the iOS release of The Walking Dead from the jump |accessdate=2013-09-17 |date=2012-07-30 |publisher=[[Penny_Arcade|Penny Arcade Report]] |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014210302/http://www.penny-arcade.com/report/article/upscaling-for-tablets-how-telltale-planned-for-the-ios-release-of-the-walki |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 历史 ==

诉说游戏在2004年成立時就已製作出初版引擎了，<ref name="telltaleprofile">{{cite web |url=http://www.adventuregamers.com/articles/view/17751 |title=A profile of Telltale Games |publisher=[[Adventure_Gamers|Adventure Gamers]] |accessdate=2013-09-17 |date=2004-10-04 |archive-date=2013-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904151608/http://www.adventuregamers.com/articles/view/17751 |dead-url=no }}</ref>引擎最初名為“诉说引擎及工具箱”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mixnmojo.com/news/Telltale-and-AG-open-shop-bank-on-character |publisher=[[Adventure_Gamers|Adventure Gamers]] |title=Telltale & AG open shop, band on character |date=2005-02-07 |accessdate=2012-10-29 |archive-date=2012-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226055457/http://mixnmojo.com/news/Telltale-and-AG-open-shop-bank-on-character |dead-url=no }}</ref>为测试引擎和分配模型，並保障第一款[[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]《{{le|骨头：走出骨头乡|Bone: Out from Boneville}}》無重大程式错误，他们先做了一款休闲扑克游戏《{{le|Telltale德州扑克|Telltale Texas Hold'em}}》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.adventuregamers.com/articles/view/17866/page2 |title=A Telltale Afternoon |date=2005-08-07 |accessdate=2013-09-17 |publisher=[[Adventure_Gamers|Adventure Gamers]] |archive-date=2013-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019115302/http://www.adventuregamers.com/articles/view/17866/page2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

诉说游戏开发每款作品都使用了Telltale Tool，該引擎从最初版本起即不断改善，比如新系统的兼容性和提升图形处理能力。<ref name="telltaleprofile" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/03/17/impressions-sam-and-max-the-devils-playhouse-the-penal-zone/ |publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] |title=Impressions: Sam & Max: The Devil's Playhouse - The Penal Zone (PS3) |date=2010-03-17 |accessdate=2013-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019143514/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/03/17/impressions-sam-and-max-the-devils-playhouse-the-penal-zone/ |archive-date=2013-10-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>迄今使用Telltale Tool开发的第三方的游戏只有《{{le|Hector: Badge of Carnage|Hector: Badge of Carnage}}》一部，該遊戲由{{le|Straandlooper|Straandlooper}}开发，並由诉说游戏发布。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mixnmojo.com/features/interviews/Straandlooper-Speaks |date=2011-06-03 |accessdate=2013-09-17 |title=Straandlooper Speaks |publisher=[[The_International_House_of_Mojo|The International House of Mojo]] |archive-date=2013-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005021237/http://mixnmojo.com/features/interviews/Straandlooper-Speaks |dead-url=no }}</ref>

